{"type": "root", "attrs": {"icon": "SHELF/followpath", "tags": "constraints"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Follow Path"], "extent": [43, 59]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Animates an object along a curve."], "extent": [59, 101]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Overview"], "extent": [101, 116], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["This tool is useful for quickly ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/anim/", "type": "link", "text": ["animating"], "fullpath": "/anim/index"}, " an object moving along a specified ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/curve", "type": "link", "text": ["path"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/curve"}, ". For example, you can make a plane fly across the sky."], "extent": [116, 281]}]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Using Follow Path Constraint"], "extent": [281, 316], "body": [{"type": "ord_group", "body": [{"blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "indent": 0, "text": ["Create the object you want to animate along a path."], "extent": [316, 372]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "indent": 0, "text": ["Use the ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "SHELF/drawcurve", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/SHELF/drawcurve"}, " ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/object/path", "type": "link", "text": ["Draw Curve tool"], "fullpath": "/object/path"}, " on the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Create"]}, " tab to to draw a curve freehand in space or on an object."], "extent": [372, 513]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "indent": 0, "text": ["Click the ", {"scheme": "Icon", "value": "SHELF/followpath", "type": "link", "text": "", "fullpath": "/shelf/SHELF/followpath"}, " Follow Path tool on the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Constraints"]}, " tab."], "extent": [513, 595]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "indent": 0, "text": ["Select the object to associate to the path and press ", {"keys": ["Enter"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, "."], "extent": [595, 662]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "indent": 0, "text": ["Select the path you want the object to follow and press ", {"keys": ["Enter"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, "."], "extent": [662, 732]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "indent": 0, "text": ["Review the ", {"scheme": null, "value": "#parameters", "type": "link", "text": ["Toolbar Parameters"], "fullpath": "/shelf/constraintpath#parameters", "fragment": "#parameters"}, " to create the constraint with or without offset."], "extent": [732, 828]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "indent": 0, "text": ["Choose the object for the look at target position and press ", {"keys": ["Enter"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " to confirm your selection or press ", {"keys": ["Enter"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " without a selection to continue without a look at target."], "extent": [828, 1004]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "ord", "indent": 0, "text": ["Choose the object for the look up target position and press ", {"keys": ["Enter"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " to confirm your selection or press ", {"keys": ["Enter"], "type": "keys", "text": null}, " without a selection to use the default up vector."], "extent": [1004, 1172]}], "container": true}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["This tool creates a new ", {"type": "code", "text": ["constraints"]}, " CHOP Network inside the object, or reuses an existing one. "], "extent": [1172, 1271]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["A ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/chop/constraintpath", "type": "link", "text": ["Follow Path CHOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/chop/constraintpath"}, " is created based on the selected objects. The constraint is added after the node that has the output flag and the output flag is moved to the new node."], "extent": [1271, 1470]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Image", "value": "/images/shelf/follow_path.jpg", "type": "img", "text": ""}], "extent": [1470, 1509]}]}, {"level": 1, "id": "parameters", "contai